{"tid":436161,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"老翁疑衝紅燈  遭兩的士撞倒輾過","createTime":"2017-10-15T02:33:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-15T12:30:19.000Z","uid":54733,"like":218,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"02f5805d6868f8bf5344de692e65cd1d7244f024","tid":436161,"uid":54733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:33:06.000Z","msg":"長沙灣興華街西與通州街交界發生車禍。凌晨約3時35分，幾部的士沿興華街西行駛，至通州街燈位紅燈停車。綠燈起步右轉通州街時，一名91歲姓馮老翁疑衝紅燈過馬路，被一部的士撞倒，老翁倒臥地上，尾隨一輛的士復將老翁輾過，並且不顧而去。<br />\n<br />\n後面另一輛的士駛至，姓黃司機發現老翁倒地，立即將車停下，以防老翁再被車輾過。而撞倒老翁之的士，肇事後已停車，姓吳40歲司機下車並準備用雨傘替老翁擋雨，不料見到輾過老翁之的士「彈一彈」及駛走，其時老翁有知覺及懂得呼痛，現場遺下一袋麵包及一隻鞋。救護員到場將老翁送院。警方調查車禍及追緝涉案的士下落。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171015/57333512\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171015%2F57333512&d=lIJcOy1SdpiccVNprGOqLb%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=dc95dab2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20171015%2F57333512&h=bcaabe4a\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20171015/57333512</a>"},{"pid":"6d7644892887d901e2965de22949714ca19df963","tid":436161,"uid":31237,"like":182,"dislike":0,"score":182,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:34:44.000Z","msg":"到底有幾多架的士"},{"pid":"2e8e8cc2715df9ce4a0025ae5cdbdf65f231af4c","tid":436161,"uid":143686,"like":34,"dislike":2,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:34:49.000Z","msg":"福氣，死都要害dc9"},{"pid":"d4527ff7cd1a14b55b4e87f46f0c3946f7b9e675","tid":436161,"uid":110207,"like":23,"dislike":1,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:36:58.000Z","msg":"想知呀伯死左未 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁樣後生仔都頂唔順啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2de6d4bb1a065bdf2fda18f349e754cbed90fab5","tid":436161,"uid":42188,"like":185,"dislike":0,"score":185,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-15T02:38:51.000Z",